title: I Entered Mr Universe - With No Training
description: In this video, Max Fosh decides to enter the Mr. Universe bodybuilding competition despite having no training or experience in bodybuilding.
summary: Max Fosh decides to enter the Mr. Universe bodybuilding competition with no training, resulting in a hilarious and unexpected outcome.
payoff: The comedic payoff comes from Max's complete lack of preparation and knowledge about bodybuilding, leading to a humorous and unexpected turn of events during the competition.
